Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That was some design contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You took first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a good design.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was such a gorgeous dress,\NI wish I could wear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Miki will let\Nyou if you ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?\NThen I'll go ask. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I haven't heard anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a bet, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your part: when you get a challenge\Nfrom St. Tail, let me know right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to cheat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to cheat!\NGeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:00:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"You Confessed?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. You're looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm sorry, I\Ncouldn't help overhearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you and Junior have a bet going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it for ice cream?\NOr maybe a hamburger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At the contest the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If Meimi isn't St. Tail,\Nthen I'll stop following her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I'm right, you have to date me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, if I prove you\Nare St. Tail, then I win the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't give up easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In y=-2x+4 reversed,\Ny equals one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, in 2x+y=4, x equals...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you make such a bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Haneoka? Miss Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you paying attention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here and solve this problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because\Nyou're always daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought we did such a good job of\Nfooling Miss Takamiya at the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd he make the bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly don't\Nwant to be caught now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you wanted to at one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, a man came\Nto me seeking help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know if I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Mr. Kanamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,His grandfather had\Nrecently passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving him a jewel in his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then some relatives rewrote the will\Nand took the jewel from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They have lied to him,\Nsaying they will put it in safekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But in actuality,\Nthey have put it up for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kanamori went to see those relatives\Nto get his jewel back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, Aunty! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, give it back! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He desperately wants to get\Nthe jewel before it is sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could help,\Nbut Miss Takamiya is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:05:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The way things are going,\Nshe and Asuka will never settle the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because St. Tail won't be caught easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But then Miss Takamiya\Nwill keep following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an excellent idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:06:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you like my hands because they\Nlook like a magician's hands, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to close my eyes,\Nyou've thought up a new trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll count to three,\Nthen you can open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama! How'd you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it? I'm sure this trick will be a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This sort of trick\Nhas been done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But never while holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely fantastic!\NShow me how to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it is the fruit of our labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say it is a symbol of our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were leaving early!\NYou're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez. And he just has\Nto have ham and eggs on Wednesdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I will visit Kanamori's house tonight\Nto steal the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's the note burnt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz it was in my breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We lure St. Tail into our trap by\Nplaying on her weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll help, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what your plan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want no part of it if it's sneaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.\NIf you won't help, I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You do want to settle our bet, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This will just be between\NSt. Tail and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Have it your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you concoct another of\Nyour strange colognes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It will come in handy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Never! Absolutely no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to go outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised, remember?\NYou said you wouldn't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going back\Non your word, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Asuka, you wait\Noutside the room. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything under control?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we guard the inside, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just the outside.\NThose are Miss Takamiya's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn that Takamiya!\NShe got her nerve, ordering me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, he's here alone. He's my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I need your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the heirloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange. Asuka Jr. isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!\NWho did this to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fooled you, didn't I?\NSaint Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka! I know you're here!\NWe're finally going to see her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The switch... is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!\NYou're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, hurry, turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm arresting her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this is St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What went wrong?\NI was right, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A moustache?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail's... a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Meimi. It's a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm taking this jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I heard St. Tail's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, probably just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The cat-burglar... I've been\Nafter all this time... is a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And a transvestite at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It can 't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"I must speak to you, but you\Nmust promise not to come close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come to D Park.\N-St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't want to see that man.\NBut I guess I'll go see what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!\NI'll bet you had quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys were trying to trap me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you were punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've had enough, don't try to\Ndiscover my identity any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it seemed like\NI was in cahoots with Takamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was nothing I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamiya made this bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If I won...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,she promised to stop\Nfollowing Haneoka around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka's one of my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, she's kind of noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't think following her\Naround all the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not why I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not why I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna arrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you want to be caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to be caught by her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If... If I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to be caught by anyone,\NI want to be caught by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief! St. Tail's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling Takamiya about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail was a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means I win the bet, Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better keep your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to be caught by anyone,\NI want to be caught by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's nowhere near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so rude!
